<div id="fragment-6">
<h3>Successful Online Learner</h3>
<hr />
<h3>To be successful online learner:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Take time to familiarize yourself with the course structure and layout in the learning management system being used such as Canvas or other technology used in the course.</li>
<li>Read the essential documents &ndash; course syllabus/course schedule.</li>
<li>Identify and establish the communication channels provided &ndash; Help Forums/online meetings/Email/groups discussion forums</li>
<li>Confirm technical requirements &ndash;so that you can access all the materials</li>
<li>Be patient and respectful of response time mentioned. Plan your time &ndash; have a personal schedule, a consistent study time and stay organized. DO NOT WAIT UNTIL THE LAST MOMENT TO WORK ON YOUR DELIVERABLES.</li>
<li>Make connections with fellow classmates and the instructor. Ask Questions &ndash; Don&rsquo;t wait.</li>
<li>Ask questions regarding expectations/content/policies. Follow the mentioned protocols for the course.</li>
<li>Log-in to the course at least 3 times in a day.</li>
</ul>
</div>
